        <summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;&quot;Agents&quot;, &quot;agentic AI&quot; are all the rage right now, but surprisingly little clarity about what it means from a programming perspective. In this post I want to survey current agentic architectures and patterns, and then try to pin it down as a programming concept. Then I&#x27;ll speculate on how programming languages will evolve to fit this new paradigm.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;</summary>
        
